code: @Override public void contribute(Info.Builder builder) {     if (camelContext != null) {         builder.withDetail("camel.name", camelContext.getName()).         builder.withDetail("camel.version", camelContext.getVersion()).         if (camelContext.getUptime() != null) {             builder.withDetail("camel.uptime", camelContext.getUptime()).             builder.withDetail("camel.uptimeMillis", camelContext.getUptimeMillis()).         }         builder.withDetail("camel.status", camelContext.getStatus().name()).     } }
